Package org.apache.drill.exec.compile

Class CheckClassVisitorFsm

java.lang.Object
org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
org.apache.drill.exec.compile.CheckClassVisitorFsm
public class CheckClassVisitorFsm extends org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
A ClassVisitor that verifies the required call sequence described in http://asm.ow2.org/asm50/javadoc/user/org/objectweb/asm/ClassVisitor.html .

There is no CheckAnnotationVisitorFsm at this time. There is no CheckFieldVisitorFsm at this time.
